review:
I have been consulting Dr.Sabina for the last 8 years since my first child was born .The diagnoses and medicines prescribed by her are so accurate .My children love visiting her .She makes the children quite comfortable for getting the vaccinations done and is very warm and friendly too .
I highly recommend her.
